 #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Web 2.0 i=
s fucking awesome. I&#8217;m writing this newsletter to you because of Web =
2.0. The probability of me figuring out how to write to all of you directly=
