ou2" style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">Building with Mo=
ney Legos</a>,</em> DeFi company Totle wrote:</p><blockquote style=3D"borde=
r-left: 4px solid #67bdfc; margin: 1em 0;"><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0; margin-left: 1em;"><em>T=
